  m_Name: NeighborJournal_17
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 34
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #17 \u2014 Sinh vi\xEAn y khoa"
  category: 3
  content: "T\xF4i l\xE0 sinh vi\xEAn y khoa n\u0103m cu\u1ED1i, \u0111ang th\u1EF1c
    t\u1EADp \u1EDF b\u1EC7nh vi\u1EC7n th\xEC d\u1ECBch b\xF9ng. T\xF4i v\u1EC1
    chung c\u01B0 v\xE0 barricade trong ph\xF2ng. T\u1EEB nh\u1EEFng g\xEC quan s\xE1t
    \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c, virus l\xE2y qua c\u1EAFn, \u1EE7 b\u1EC7nh 4-6 gi\u1EDD.
    Bi\u1EC3u hi\u1EC7n: m\u1EAFt tr\u1EAFng, m\u1EA5t \xFD th\u1EE9c, hung d\u1EEF.
    T\xF4i nghi ng\u1EDD \u0111\xE2y l\xE0 bi\u1EBFn th\u1EC3 c\u1EE7a virus rage
    \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c ch\u1EC9nh s\u1EEDa. N\u1EBFu c\xF3 ai \u0111ang
    nghi\xEAn c\u1EE9u thu\u1ED1c gi\u1EA3i, h\xE3y li\xEAn h\u1EC7 t\u1EA7n s\u1ED1
    radio 87.5. T\xF4i c\xF3 ki\u1EBFn th\u1EE9c y khoa, c\xF3 th\u1EC3 gi\xFAp \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
